law.text:
The provisions of this subtitle do not apply to:
If it contains a code indicating the date of manufacture, a package or packaging component that was manufactured prior to July 1, 1993;
Until July 1, 1997, a package and packaging component that would not exceed the concentration levels set forth in § 9-1902 of this subtitle but for the addition of recycled materials;
A package or packaging component conditionally exempt under § 9-1904 of this subtitle; and
Any alcoholic beverage bottled before October 1, 1992.
